 items-center gap-2"><code class="flex-1 rounded-md border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/50 px-3 py-2 font-mono text-sm text-pink-300">$ <!-- -->bun ./index.ts</code></div></a><ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-2 px-6 pb-6"><li class="flex items-start text-sm"><span class="mr-1.5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-pink-400">✓</span><a href="/docs/runtime/nodejs-apis" class="text-gray-300 underline decoration-gray-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-pink-300 hover:decoration-pink-400">Node.js API compatibility</a></li><li class="flex items-start text-sm"><span class="mr-1.5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-pink-400">✓</span><a href="/docs/runtime/typescript" class="text-gray-300 underline decoration-gray-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-pink-300 hover:decoration-pink-400">TypeScript, JSX &amp; React (zero config)</a></li><li class="flex items-start text-sm"><span class="mr-1.5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-pink-400">✓</span><a href="/docs/api/fetch" class="text-gray-300 underline decoration-gray-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-pink-300 hover:decoration-pink-400">Comprehensive builtin standard library</a></li><li class="flex items-start text-sm"><span class="mr-1.5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-pink-400">✓</span><a href="/docs/api/sql" class="text-gray-300 underline decoration-gray-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-pink-300 hover:decoration-pink-400">PostgreSQL, Redis, MySQL, SQLite</a></li><li class="flex items-start text-sm"><span class="mr-1.5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-pink-400">✓</span><a href="/docs/cli/run" class="text-gray-300 underline decoration-gray-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-pink-300 hover:decoration-pink-400">Hot &amp; watch mode built-in</a></li><li class="flex items-start text-sm"><span class="mr-1.5 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 text-pink-400">✓</span><a href="/docs/runtime/env" class="text-gray-300 underline decoration-gray-600 underline-offset-2 transition-colors hover:text-pink-300